usage: evaluation_autorun.py [-h] [--config CONFIG] [--list] [--dry-run]
                             [--job JOB]

Evaluation AutoRun Orchestrator — validate and run evaluation jobs

options:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --config CONFIG  Path to YAML config file
  --list           List jobs as JSON
  --dry-run        Validate config without running
  --job JOB        Filter to a specific job name
